This is the area corresponding to the South Anchorage Sea, it is situated directly south the naval base and is unlocked from the start of the game. This area is inspired from [[Winter 2015 Event]].<br>
There is one repair dock on this hexagon and is expandable up to three.<br>
:Clearing the third map of this area (V7-3), alongside [[Kancolle Kai:Sandbox/Area 4#/V4-1|V4-1]] gives access to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 5#/V5-1|V5-1]] ('''南方海域''').
:Fully clearing this area, alongside [[Kancolle Kai:Sandbox/Area 5#/V5-3|V5-3]] gives access to [[KanColle Kai:Sandbox/Area 5#/V5-4|V5-4]] ('''南方海域''').

